
flowchart TB
  U[User\nScenario text OR Rough-draft PDF] --> CS["Copilot Studio Agent\nArticle Forge (KB Orchestrator)"]

  subgraph CSO[Copilot Studio Orchestration]
    CS --> R[KB – Entry Router\nAmbiguity Rules + Deterministic Formatting]
    R --> O1["Output 1\nMSP KB Article (Markdown)\nCanonical"]
    R --> O2[Output 2\nSharePoint Page Content\nPlain text]
    R --> O3[Output 3\nWord Doc Content\nTemplate-ready plain text]
  end

  subgraph G["Grounding Sources (Conceptual)"]
    ED["Enterprise knowledge\n(approved internal docs/KB)"]:::src
    MS["Microsoft authoritative resources\n(product behavior, UI labels, caveats)"]:::src
    GK["General technical knowledge\n(safe patterns for common issues)"]:::src
  end

  CS --- ED
  CS --- MS
  CS --- GK

  O1 --> REV["Review / Approval\n(IT knowledge owner)"]
  O2 --> PUB[Publish Trigger\nUser selects Continue]
  PUB --> AF[Azure Function\nPublishKbToSharePoint]
  AF --> SP[SharePoint KB Site\nPage created/updated]

